{"id":4108,"date":"2025-06-14T14:39:44","date_gmt":"2025-06-14T07:39:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4108"},"modified":"2025-06-14T14:39:44","modified_gmt":"2025-06-14T07:39:44","slug":"tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ea1i sao t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc\/\"><b><i>T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc <\/i><\/b><\/a><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng trong chu tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp s\u1eebng gi\u00e0 c\u1ed7i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p v\u1eadt l\u00fd hay h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc. T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng enzyme ho\u1eb7c acid t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. V\u1eady c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y ra sao. C\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft kh\u00e1c. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc-la-gi\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 enzyme tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y, acid t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt\u2026 Nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 thu nh\u1ecf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u00e0n da m\u1edbi. Nh\u1edd c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc-va-chu-trinh-tai-tao-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 chu tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ti\u00eau s\u1eebng trong t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf t\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp s\u1eebng m\u1edbi nhanh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi chu k\u1ef3 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean (kho\u1ea3ng 4 tu\u1ea7n). \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da s\u1ea1m m\u00e0u, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, gi\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec5m khu\u1ea9n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0o chu tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uu-diem-noi-bat-cua-tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc\"><\/span><b>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">So v\u1edbi t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft v\u1eadt l\u00fd. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. Nh\u1edd c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4109\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4109\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4109\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-1.webp\" alt=\"\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4109\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng enzyme v\u00e0 acid c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt. Gi\u00fap ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, l\u00e0n da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da: Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp s\u1eebng gi\u00e0 c\u1ed7i. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y c\u00f2n k\u00edch th\u00edch qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n sinh t\u1ebf b\u00e0o m\u1edbi. Gi\u00fap da tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef g\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da: Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c b\u00e0o m\u00f2n da, t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: Do kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a h\u1ea1t scrub hay acid c\u00f3 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ea1nh. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y an to\u00e0n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, da sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c da m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-quan-trong-khi-su-dung-tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p an to\u00e0n, b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4111\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4111\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4111\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-3.webp\" alt=\"L\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4111\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u01b0u \u00fd quan tr\u1ecdng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m. Ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2-3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m m\u1ecfng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng sau khi t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu \u0111ang d\u00f9ng Retinol ho\u1eb7c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb. N\u00ean t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u uy t\u00edn. C\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"so-sanh-3-phuong-phap-tay-da-chet-vat-ly-hoa-hoc-va-sinh-hoc\"><\/span><b>So s\u00e1nh 3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft: V\u1eadt l\u00fd, H\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 Sinh h\u1ecdc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f3 ba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn: t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft v\u1eadt l\u00fd, t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc. M\u1ed7i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ri\u00eang. Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c nhau. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng so s\u00e1nh chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4110\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4110\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4110\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-2.webp\" alt=\"V\u1eadt l\u00fd, H\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 Sinh h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"909\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-2-264x300.webp 264w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-2-768x873.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/47-2-600x682.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4110\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">V\u1eadt l\u00fd, H\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 Sinh h\u1ecdc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft v\u1eadt l\u00fd<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ea1t scrub, b\u00e0n ch\u1ea3i ho\u1eb7c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c acid nh\u01b0 AHA, BHA, PHA \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, gi\u00fap da bong tr\u00f3c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng enzyme ho\u1eb7c acid t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean l\u1edbp da ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn da m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, gi\u00fap da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng ngay sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; D\u1ec5 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian th\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao v\u1edbi da d\u1ea7u, m\u1ee5n nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da, gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; D\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; N\u1ebfu h\u1ea1t scrub qu\u00e1 to ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 da th\u00edch nghi.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u1eadm h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u1ea7n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lo\u1ea1i da ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da th\u01b0\u1eddng, da h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p, da \u00edt nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u, da m\u1ee5n, da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, c\u00f3 l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da y\u1ebfu, da sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1-2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n (t\u00f9y v\u00e0o n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 acid)<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nen-chon-phuong-phap-tay-da-chet-nao\"><\/span><b>N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft n\u00e0o?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe, \u00edt nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft v\u1eadt l\u00fd, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 h\u1ea1t m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 thao t\u00e1c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu da d\u1ea7u, m\u1ee5n, c\u00f3 l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to: T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u v\u00ec gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng: T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u00ec t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4093\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4093\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4093\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-thumb.webp\" alt=\"Kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc GSC Natural Peeling\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-thumb.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-thumb-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-thumb-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-thumb-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-thumb-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4093\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc GSC Natural Peeling<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng hay t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u00e3y l\u1eafng nghe l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t! Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc m\u00e0 GSC chia s\u1ebb. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap cho n\u00e0ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng enzyme ho\u1eb7c acid t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. V\u1eady c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y ra sao. C\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft kh\u00e1c. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4112,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4108","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4108","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4108"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4108\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4113,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4108\/revisions\/4113"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4112"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4108"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4108"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4108"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}